function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	for i = 1, #tPlayers do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_TreeWhispers4, tPlayers[i])
	end
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(conv_TreeWhispers4)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_AmbushBreak1, idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(conv_AmbushBreak1)
	Hydra.EventSend("Ambush02NextAmbushWave")
	
	local tPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()

	for i = 1, #tPlayers do
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_TreeWhispers7, tPlayers[i])
	end

	
	

end

function Start(idActor, snoQuest)

	tAmbushTrapSpawns = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Bog_Ambush02Traps")
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	if #tAmbushTrapSpawns > 0 then
		for i, GhostTrap in ipairs(tAmbushTrapSpawns) do
			Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(GhostTrap, 1)
		end
	end
	
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idNeyrelleFollower)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_NeyrelleSnakeMove, idNeyrelleFollower)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idNeyrelleFollower)

	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelleFollower, NeyrelleSnakeDoorLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorathFollower, LorathSnakeDoorLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(conv_NeyrelleSnakeMove)
	

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(idLorathFollower, "AnimKey_Neutral")
	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(idNeyrelleFollower, "AnimKey_Neutral")
	Hydra.QActorEnableAI(idLorathFollower, true)
	Hydra.QActorEnableAI(idNeyrelleFollower, true)
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.25)

	Hydra.EventSend("BeginAmbushVignette2")
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_GhostFightBark, idLorathFollower)

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	-- Immediately turning the trigger off to avoid multiple
	-- triggerings while the script is running
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(idSnakeSegment)
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.QActorSheath(idNeyrelleFollower)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelleFollower, NeyrelleRunLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idNeyrelleFollower, NeyrelleRunLoc, true)
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorathFollower, LorathRunLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorathFollower, LorathRunLoc, true)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idNeyrelleFollower)
	Hydra.EventSend("DoorOpen")
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	Hydra.ActorDelete(idNeyrelleFollower)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idLorathFollower)
	
end

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.Wait(2)

	idLorathFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	idNeyrelleFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_Magic")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLorathFollower) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idNeyrelleFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idLorathFollower)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idNeyrelleFollower)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	SetTraversalEnabled(idTraversalKiller, true)
	
	idLorathFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLorathFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idLorathFollower)
		Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idLorathFollower)
	end
	
	idNeyrelleFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_Magic")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idNeyrelleFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idNeyrelleFollower)
		Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idNeyrelleFollower)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLorathFollower) then
		-- Lorath Actions
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorathFollower, LorathDuckUnderLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLorathFollower)
		Hydra.QActorPower(idLorathFollower, powerTraversal, idDuckUnderTraversal, true)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLorathFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorathFollower, idGroveTrigger, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorathFollower, idGroveTrigger, true)
	end

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idNeyrelleFollower) then
		-- Neyrelle Actions
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelleFollower, LorathDuckUnderLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idNeyrelleFollower)
		Hydra.QActorPower(idNeyrelleFollower, powerTraversal, idDuckUnderTraversal, true)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelleFollower, NeyrelleWaitLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idNeyrelleFollower, NeyrelleWaitLoc, true)
	end
		
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	idLorathFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	idNeyrelleFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_Magic")
	
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idNeyrelleFollower)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelleFollower, NeyrelleStandLoc01, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idNeyrelleFollower, NeyrelleStandLoc01, true)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorathFollower, idActorDetector, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorathFollower, idActorDetector, true)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idLorathFollower)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idNeyrelleFollower)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_LorathWound, idNeyrelleFollower)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(conv_LorathWound)
	
	--Hydra.EventSend("FoundWoundedSnake")

end

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	idLorathFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	idNeyrelleFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_Magic")
	
	Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idFallenTrees, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idFallenTrees, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idFallenTrees, true)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLorathFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idLorathFollower)
		Hydra.ActorAIForcePrimaryTarget(idLorathFollower, idFallenTrees)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idNeyrelleFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idNeyrelleFollower)
		Hydra.ActorAIForcePrimaryTarget(idNeyrelleFollower, idFallenTrees)
	end
	
end

Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(idNeyrelleFollower, "AnimKey_Stunned")

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	
	idLorathFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	idNeyrelleFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Neyrelle_Follower_Magic")
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLorathFollower) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idNeyrelleFollower) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_LostSnake, idNeyrelleFollower, idLorathFollower)
		Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(conv_LostSnake)
		bSnakeSearch = true
	end
	

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	if bSnakeSearch then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_FoundSnake, idNeyrelleFollower)
	end
	
end
